text: Diadelia inornata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1905.BioLib.cz - Diadelia inornata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1905 Category:Taxa named by Léon Fairmaire
